long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The extension doesn't require any access to your account - it just checks if the like button is clicked and if it's not, it clicks it.

I made this because sometimes I end up watching videos I have already seen.

GitLab: https://gitlab.com/b.m.steponavicius/you_liked_it
